      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      List<String> cookiesToShow
      defines the cookies that we want to render for the documentation for this case: its the default declaration and no cookies are declared if you want to define cookies to display for a request, you HAVE TO override this list in your test If you want to see all the cookies, you have to set cookiesToShow = SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS IMPORTANT: you don't have to care about the case of the cookies name
      static DocTestMachine docTestMachine 
      List<String> headersToShow
      defines the headers that we want to render for the documentation for this case: its the default declaration and no headers are declared if you want to define headers to display for a request and response, you HAVE TO override this list in your test If you want to see all the headers, you have to set headersToShow = SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS IMPORTANT: you don't have to care about the case of the headers name
      static List<String> SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS
      Constant used to show all the elements of a list e.g cookiesToShow or headersToShow.

      • SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS

        public static final List<String> SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS
        Constant used to show all the elements of a list e.g cookiesToShow or headersToShow. Just set this list equals to this SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS

      • docTestMachine

        public static DocTestMachine docTestMachine

      • cookiesToShow

        public List<String> cookiesToShow
        defines the cookies that we want to render for the documentation for this case: its the default declaration and no cookies are declared if you want to define cookies to display for a request, you HAVE TO override this list in your test

        If you want to see all the cookies, you have to set cookiesToShow = SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS

        IMPORTANT: you don't have to care about the case of the cookies name

      • headersToShow

        public List<String> headersToShow
        defines the headers that we want to render for the documentation for this case: its the default declaration and no headers are declared if you want to define headers to display for a request and response, you HAVE TO override this list in your test

        If you want to see all the headers, you have to set headersToShow = SHOW_ALL_ELEMENTS

        IMPORTANT: you don't have to care about the case of the headers name

                          Object result,
